To build a WRE on RedHat Enterprise Linux or CentOS. Do the following tasks:

1) Install packages for MySQL, Apache, nginx, and perl.

yum install -y mysql55
\ httpd-server httpd-devel mod_ssl mod_perl mod_perl-devel
\ perl gcc cpp glibc cmake

2) Update the default my.cnf file.  A suggested one is in var/setupfiles/my.cnf

3) Install WebGUI's perl support libraries

cpan App::Cpanminus
cpanm Task::WebGUI

4) Import the WRE into your environment:
 . wre/sbin/setenvironment.sh

